is with Polyangiitis (GPA).","dimension":8,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.037964,0.069247,0.080531,0.093107,0.10245,0.10377,0.10345,0.095523,0.086009,0.08899,0.070934,0.068032],"unified_progress":[0.04403,0.05788,0.078512,0.089443,0.095742,0.10429,0.10203,0.10067,0.095511,0.090665,0.076334,0.064898]},{"section":11,"text":"GPA typically affects the upper airways, lungs, and kidneys.","dimension":6,"group":2,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.026756,0.060254,0.076128,0.090034,0.10045,0.10421,0.108,0.10186,0.095457,0.093331,0.079272,0.064235],"unified_progress":[0.081102,0.06127,0.075362,0.085519,0.092469,0.098158,0.098237,0.099035,0.093099,0.088719,0.07166,0.055371]},{"section":12,"text":"The classic triad is rhinitis/sinusitis, pulmonary infiltrates (sometimes cavitating), and glomerulonephritis.","dimension":8,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.029125,0.063801,0.076351,0.08876,0.097889,0.10318,0.10547,0.10034,0.093968,0.094969,0.078037,0.068114],"unified_progress":[0.035061,0.06129,0.085677,0.092534,0.098121,0.1059,0.10378,0.1009,0.096784,0.089984,0.07312,0.056844]},{"section":13,"text":"The renal biopsy findings fit with pauci-immune crescentic GN, which is common in GPA.","dimension":8,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.031638,0.06693,0.08055,0.090744,0.096404,0.098462,0.10073,0.095968,0.092302,0.09224,0.079319,0.074717],"unified_progress":[0.036314,0.061037,0.079496,0.091347,0.097295,0.10334,0.10126,0.099165,0.096093,0.090065,0.078331,0.066264]},{"section":14,"text":"Also, the cold-like nasal symptoms could be chronic sinusitis.","dimension":9,"group":9,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.031079,0.067401,0.078676,0.086619,0.092668,0.098001,0.099902,0.098189,0.097344,0.092221,0.084611,0.073288],"unified_progress":[0.040455,0.065376,0.077568,0.086564,0.093534,0.098672,0.097916,0.098454,0.09835,0.093238,0.083053,0.066819]},{"section":15,"text":"The hemoptysis is another pulmonary manifestation.","di